data.description: ASSUMABLE VA MORTGAGE! Spacious, half acre lot located on Amelia Island. Screened in POOL and HOT TUB, the perfect place to entertain or simply unwind. Peaceful mornings and stunning sunsets on your own private oasis.  The home's location on the island allows for the coastal lifestyle you've always dreamed of. Public beach access is just minutes away from the front door. The upgrades throughout the home and vaulted ceilings create an open atmosphere. The single-story home features two ensuites, ideal for guests. The flex room can be used for an art studio, play room, crafting, office space - plenty of room to customize the space to meet your needs. The property is surrounded by lush tropical landscaping and majestic oaks. The established Fernandina Beach Golf Course neighborhood offers a community vibe with NO HOA regulations, you'll have the freedom to make this house and yard your own. Begin making ISLAND MEMORIES!
